.br
Reply = ok | {error, \fBreason()\fR\&} | \fBinput_reply()\fR\& | \fBoutput_reply()\fR\&
.br
.RE
.RE
.RS
.LP
Sorts tuples on files\&.
.LP
\fIkeysort(N, FileName)\fR\& is equivalent to \fIkeysort(N, [FileName], FileName)\fR\&\&.
.RE
.LP
.nf

